<ul>
	<li>General office setting—no hazardous chemicals or manufacturing equipment/production lines/machinery, however, noise levels fluctuate with open office environment</li>
	<li>Minimal travel</li>
	<li>Sitting\standing (75%) of the day at meetings and at desk</li>
	<li>Lecturing (15%)</li>
	<li>Keyboarding and using mouse (90%)</li>
	<li>Occasional stooping and reaching (5%)</li>
	<li>Reading (90%)</li>
</ul>
